## Compliance Checklist

Use during Phase 6b (Quality Audit) and design reviews:

### Tokens and Values
- [ ] All color values use semantic tokens (DS-002, DS-003)
- [ ] All spacing values use spacing scale tokens (DS-005)
- [ ] All text uses typography scale tokens (DS-004)
- [ ] No font weight other than 400 and 500 anywhere in the system (DS-004)
- [ ] No hardcoded hex, px, or raw values in component definitions

### Components
- [ ] All components documented per DS-007 (including responsive behavior)
- [ ] All interactive states designed per DS-009 (including Selected state)
- [ ] Required patterns defined for all applicable scenarios (DS-010)
- [ ] Icons from a single source with accessible labels (DS-011)

### Accessibility
- [ ] WCAG 2.1 AA verified for all text/background combinations
- [ ] Status never communicated by color alone (icon + text always) (DS-003)
- [ ] Focus ring visible on all interactive elements
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44×44px on mobile (DS-020)

### Design System Documents
- [ ] `docs/design-system/VISUAL-DIRECTION.md` exists with all sections complete (DS-016)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/PILLAR-PROFILES.md` exists with a profile for each pillar (DS-018)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/PAGE-ARCHETYPES.md` exists with all archetypes (DS-019)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/DESIGN-TOKENS.md` exists with 3 token layers + Tailwind mapping (DS-002)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/RESPONSIVE-SYSTEM.md` exists with breakpoints and grid (DS-020)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/COMPONENT-LIBRARY.md` exists with all components (DS-007)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/INTERACTION-PATTERNS.md` exists with required patterns (DS-010)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/CONTENT-RENDERING.md` exists if the system renders authored content (DS-021)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/LLM-QUICKREF.md` exists and is up to date (DS-022)
- [ ] `docs/design-system/IMAGE-PROMPTS.md` exists or is explicitly marked not applicable (DS-017)

### Visual Calibration
- [ ] Aesthetic Archetype defined and unambiguous (DS-016)
- [ ] Anti-Patterns section contains ≥ 5 specific items (DS-016)
- [ ] Extension Guidelines section contains ≥ 4 numbered rules (DS-016)
- [ ] Calibration Checklist section contains ≥ 6 questions (DS-016)
- [ ] Pillar tokens overridden per app/pillar (DS-018)
- [ ] Every page classified in a page archetype (DS-019)

